{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "systeam-gestion-proyectos-v2",
    "name": "Systeam API — Gestión de Proyectos",
    "description": "Batería completa de tests para la API Systeam.\n\nServicios:\n- API Principal: http://localhost:8081\n- Auth Service: http://localhost:8080\n\nFlujo de ejecución:\n1. Ejecutar carpeta '🔧 Setup' completa (crea usuarios de prueba y guarda tokens)\n2. Ejecutar el resto de carpetas en orden\n\nUsuario bootstrap (del seed de BD):\n- email: admin@ideafy.local\n- password: password\n- rol: ADMIN (todos los permisos)\n\nNota: el setup registra un usuario 'plain' sin roles para los tests de 403.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",        "value": "http://localhost:8081", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "auth_url",        "value": "http://localhost:8090", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token",           "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plain_token",     "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plain_user_id",   "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "project_id",      "value": "1",  "type": "string" },
    { "key": "investment_id",   "value": "1",  "type": "string" },
    { "key": "dividendo_id",    "value": "1",  "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔧 Setup (ejecutar primero)",
      "description": "Crea los usuarios de prueba y guarda los tokens en variables de colección. Correr en orden de arriba a abajo.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "1. Login ADMIN",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{auth_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{auth_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"postman.admin@systeam.com\",\n  \"password\": \"PostmanAdmin123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "type": "text/javascript",
              "exec": [
                "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                "",
                "pm.test('Login ADMIN exitoso — accessToken guardado', function () {",
                "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                "    pm.expect(json.accessToken, 'accessToken debe existir').to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.accessToken);",
                "    console.log('✅ Token ADMIN guardado');",
                "    console.log('Roles:', JSON.stringify(json.roles));",
                "    console.log('Permissions:', JSON.stringify(json.permissions));",
                "});"
              ]
            }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "2. Registrar usuario plain (sin roles)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{auth_url}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{auth_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Test Plain User\",\n  \"email\": \"plainuser@test.systeam\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "type": "text/javascript",
              "exec": [
                "const code = pm.response.code;",
                "",
                "pm.test('Registro exitoso (201) o usuario ya existe (409)', function () {",
                "    pm.expect([201, 409]).to.include(code);",
                "});",
                "",
                "if (code === 201) {",
                "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                "    pm.collectionVariables.set('plain_user_id', String(json.id));",
                "    console.log('✅ plain_user_id: ' + json.id);",
                "} else {",
                "    console.log('Usuario ya existía — continuar con login');",
                "}"
              ]
            }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "3. Login usuario plain",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{auth_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{auth_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"plainuser@test.systeam\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "type": "text/javascript",
              "exec": [
                "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                "",
                "pm.test('Token plain user guardado', function () {",
                "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                "    pm.expect(json.accessToken).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                "    pm.collectionVariables.set('plain_token', json.accessToken);",
                "    console.log('✅ plain_token guardado. Roles:', JSON.stringify(json.roles));",
                "});"
              ]
            }
          }]
        }

      ]
    },

